<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>61</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Tiva dawh luannak nelrawn tha ah siseh, Rili tilet a thomi lakah
 siseh, Khamhbawi Jesuh nih a ka hruainak kip ah, Thawngtha bia chim ah
 lunglawmin ka kal lai.

[C1]
   Khamhbawi hruainak kip ah, Lunglawm in ka kal lai, Khamhbawi nih a
   ka hruainak ah lawm in ka kal lai.

[V2]
 Lam harnak lungpang le horkuang ah siseh, Totho lak le thlichia hrang
 lakah siseh, A hawi sin in a tlaumi tuu kawl awkah, Khamhbawi a ka hruai
 ahcun ka kal ko lai.

[C2]
   Khamhbawi hruainak kip ah, Lunglawm in ka kal lai, Khamhbawi nih a
   ka hruainak ah lawm in ka kal lai.

[V3]
 Khamhbawi a ka hruainak kip ah ka zulh lai, Lawmh le ngaihchiat zongah
 a nawl ka ngaih lai, Himnak lam kha amah nih cun a hngalh i, Ni bang a
 ceumi inn ah a ka kalpi.

[C3]
   Khamhbawi hruainak kip ah, Lunglawm in ka kal lai, Khamhbawi nih a
   ka hruainak ah lawm in ka kal lai.</lyrics>
<key>Eb</key>
<title>KHAMHBAWI HRUAINAK KIP AH CH61</title>
</song>